sellerCard.description:
Welcome to my profile!

I am a full stack web developer with 4+ years of experience in building and maintaining web applications. I specialize in HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, JavaScript, React, Vue, PHP, Laravel, Node js and Nuxt js to create custom and user friendly web experiences.

I am passionate about my work and I am always looking for new and innovative ways to improve my skills and knowledge. I am also a strong believer in communication and collaboration, and I always work closely with my clients to ensure that their needs are met and exceeded.

description.content:
Welcome to: Reliable and skilled full stack web developer


I will design,redesign,build or rebuild your website with a focus on performance, scalability, and modern design


With extensive experience in HTML CSS, REACT JS NEXT.JS, PHP LARAVEL etc. I specialize in delivering high-quality, responsive, and secure websites that perfectly align with your business goals.


Frontend Development: HTML, CSS, JavaScript,Tailwind CSS, Bootstrap, React Next js

Backend Development: PHP LARAVEL NODE.JS MYSQL Database


Services Included:


  • Full stack web development from scratch
  • Website redesigns and revamps to modern standards
  • Bug fixing, troubleshooting, and performance optimization
  • Custom web applications and API integration
  • E-commerce websites, dashboards, and admin panels
  • Secure, scalable backend development with PHP Laravel


Why Me?


  • Responsive Design
  • User-friendly design
  • Unlimited Revisions
  • 100% Quality Code
  • Animations & Transitions


Lets collaborate to create the perfect web solution for your business! Drop me a message to get started.


Laravel development,PHP development,HTML CSS,react.js front end web developer,API development,Back-end development,Laravel migration,Laravel optimization

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you implement specific functionalities, such as forms or sliders, into the HTML?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I can integrate various functionalities into your HTML, including forms, sliders, galleries, and more, based on your requirements.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What if I need additional pages or sections added to the website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I offer additional page or section creation as part of my services. Simply let me know your requirements, and I'll provide a custom quote based on the scope of work.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will you make the website responsive?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: YES. I will make fully responsive website for you.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will you provide me the source file?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes! I will provide all the custom assets/files.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What is your experience with Laravel development?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I have 4 years of experience working with Laravel, building a variety of web applications ranging from simple landing pages to complex e-commerce platforms.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you handle projects of any size?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I can handle projects of all sizes. Whether you need a small landing page or a large-scale enterprise application, I have the skills and experience to deliver quality results.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How do you handle project deadlines?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I work closely with my clients to establish clear project timelines and expectations. I prioritize efficient work practices and effective communication to ensure projects are completed on time.

reviews.comment: Waleed Khalid delivered an EXCEPTIONAL website development experience with his keen attention to detail and expert coding skills, ensuring a bug-free outcome. His proactive communication and high level of cooperation made the process smooth and enjoyable, as he truly went above and beyond expectations. Working with Waleed was a pleasure—highly recommended! 👏

Waleed Khalid truly impressed with exceptional professionalism and bug-free work. His understanding and proactive  communication made the website development process seamless, always delivering on time. Waleed is an excellent web designer, and I am looking forward to working on future projects 👏

Waleed's React JS pricing card design is exceptional! The layout is clean, modern, and visually appealing, offering an intuitive user experience. His attention to detail and skill in creating responsive, user-friendly designs make him a standout in the field. Highly recommended!

Absolutely amazing! I cant think of anyone better to have worked with. Clear communication, knows exactly what you need and delivers innovative and original work. I'll definitely be working with Waleed again. Cant thank him enough !!!

Waleed Khalid delivered an outstanding website development experience! His work was bug-free and highly professional with meticulous attention to detail. Working with him was a breeze due to his deep understanding, excellent cooperation, and politeness. Highly recommend! 🙌

reviews_snippet.comment: I had some complicated design, that other developers rejected or even canceled the job halfway through. But Waleed could make it work! He did not give up on this. If you ever need some coding done, this is the right man for the job!

Waleed is an exceptional Fiverr seller who created a beautifully crafted healthcare website for me. His expertise in HTML and CSS is evident in every detail of the site. Beyond his technical skills, Waleed's communication throughout the project was clear and proactive. He listened attentively to my requirements and delivered a website that exceeded my expectations. I highly recommend this seller for anyone seeking top-notch web development services.

Great experience.  First step it was 4pm my time and my request was answered immediately so I thought it must be the AI response.  Nope, Waleed himself which surprised me.  Within 5 minutes we were on a google chat going over the specifics.  Great job listening and sharing screens so everything was understood from the start.  I woke up this morning and my new HTML code was sitting waiting in my inbox at fiverr.  Fixed up and altered to address my issues.  Actually beautiful how this worked so well.
